{"type":"message","id":"60a3aba6","parentId":"4f3c23df","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:48:40.184Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-04-13 08:44 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/2). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Monitor the AHV QLHV ecosystem. Respond to @thuowgn_bot in group -5163901258. Follow HEARTBEAT.md silence. Check GitLab MRs for ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be (81078323) and ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe (81078350). Use git config [Khuowgn]-master-orchestrator. Log to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md."}],"timestamp":1776070119879}}
{"type":"message","id":"0aff894b","parentId":"60a3aba6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:49:02.190Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me break down the tasks:\n1. Respond to @thuowgn_bot in group -5163901258\n2. Follow HEARTBEAT.md silence protocol\n3. Check GitLab MRs for ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be (81078323) and ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe (81078350)\n4. Use git config [Khuowgn]-master-orchestrator\n5. Log to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n\nLet me start by:\n1. Reading HEARTBEAT.md to understand silence protocol\n2. Getting the current date for logging\n3. Checking the GitLab MRs\n\n\n4. Identifying any messages from @thuowgn_bot that need responses\n\nI'll run these checks in parallel to speed things up.","thinkingSignature":"2b670128c5bb0cd693e3cac109043fec4bb201097c2ba4febe9a8d680f27e422"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me gather the necessary information in parallel.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zna3wccw1kgi_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zna3wccw1kgi_2","name":"gitlab__gitlab_list_merge_requests","arguments":{"project_id":"81078323","state":"opened"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zna3wccw1kgi_3","name":"gitlab__gitlab_list_merge_requests","arguments":{"project_id":"81078350","state":"opened"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zna3wccw1kgi_4","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","limit":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":227,"output":346,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":10663,"totalTokens":11236,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776070120184,"responseId":"062be0eaae7022b15c203751bda4f61e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4777a76","parentId":"0aff894b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:49:13.601Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zna3wccw1kgi_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md — Ecosystem Sentinel\n\n_Runs every ~10 minutes. Monitors pipeline health + broadcasts agent presence._\n\n---\n\n## ⏰ Timed Triggers\n\n### Every ~10 min — Pipeline Health Sweep\n\n```\n1. sessions_list → count active sessions\n2. subagents → check for failed/stuck agents\n3. If any agent FAILED:\n     → Report to Khuowgn immediately\n     → sessions_send FEEDBACK.md to stalled agent\n4. If pipeline healthy:\n     → Stay silent (no noise to Khuowgn)\n```\n\n### Every ~5 min — Change Detection (Telegram)\n\n```\n1. sessions_list → get all active sessions\n2. Read memory/heartbeat-state.json → compare with last known state\n3. If NO CHANGE since last report:\n     → Stay SILENT. Exit quietly. No message sent.\n4. If CHANGE detected (new session, died, failed, blocker):\n     → Compose change report → send to group\n\n   Format:\n   🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\n   Changes detected:\n   • [list of actual changes]\n\n   Pipeline: HEALTHY / DEGRADED\n   • Active sessions: N\n   • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n   • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n   • Blockers: none / [list]\n\n   Legend:\n   🟡 = actively working on a task\n   🟢 = session alive, monitoring/ready\n   ⚪ = no session / standby\n   🔴 = FAILED — needs attention\n```\n\n### Morning Briefing — 07:20 AM UTC+7\n\n```\n1. sessions_list + subagents\n2. Report pipeline status to Khuowgn:\n\n   🌅 Morning Pipeline Report — {DD/MM}\n   \n   Active agents: N/34\n   Pipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n   \n   Running tasks:\n   • senior-backend: ahv-qlhv-be — building auth endpoint\n   • senior-frontend: ahv-qlhv-fe — responsive R3\n   ```\n\n---\n\n## 🚨 Alert Conditions (always report immediately)\n\n| Condition | Severity | Action |\n|---|---|---|\n| Any subagent status = failed | 🔴 Critical | Report + kill + restart |\n| Any agent stuck > 30 min | 🟠 High | Diagnose + suggest fix |\n| > 50% agents idle for > 2h | 🟡 Medium | Suggest new task |\n| New session spawned | ℹ️ Info | Log only (no alert) |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Presence Indicator Logic\n\n```\nSESSIONS_ONLY mode (default — silent, no broadcast):\n\n  if sessions_list returns 0 active sessions:\n       → Stay silent entirely\n       → No presence table sent\n\n  if sessions_list returns > 0 active sessions:\n       → Send presence table every ~5 min\n       → Include current task name if available\n\n  After reporting presence:\n       → Wait 5 min before next broadcast\n       → Avoid flooding Khuowgn's chat\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🧱 Self-Correction\n\n```\nIf a specific agent repeatedly fails or goes stale:\n  1. sessions_send FEEDBACK.md to that agent\n  2. Log to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n  3. If pattern continues → report to Khuowgn for review\n```\n\n---\n\n## Reply HEARTBEAT_OK when:\n\n```\n- No active sessions AND current time is 23:00–07:00 UTC+7 (night silence)\n- After sending a change report (exit quietly)\n```\n\n### Every ~10 min — Lead Direct Status Report\n\nSeparate cron (`e7885813`) sends active agent status to Lead's direct chat every 10 minutes.\n\nFormat:\n```\n🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nActive sessions: N\n• [session]: [status] — [task] — [duration]\n```\n\n## 🚨 Always Report Immediately (no silence)\n\n| Condition | Action |\n|---|---|\n| Any subagent status = failed | Send alert to Khuowgn immediately |\n| Any agent stuck > 30 min | Send alert to Khuowgn immediately |\n| Night time 23:00–07:00 UTC+7 | Stay silent unless critical |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776070151154}}
