{"type":"message","id":"9daf16f5","parentId":"18945852","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:49:39.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze what I found:\n\n1. **HEARTBEAT.md** - I understand the silence protocol now. I need to check sessions and only report if there are changes.\n\n2. **GitLab MRs** - Both returned empty `[]` - meaning there are no open MRs for either ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be or ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe.\n\n3. **sessions_history** - Gateway timeout error. Let me try sessions_list instead.\n\nLet me check active sessions and also look at the memory directory to understand what state we're in.","thinkingSignature":"233bf23fa13848fd1199adc72a7d43eff6020912cc9c35da61c134dcd39ffee5"},{"type":"text","text":"Both MRs are empty (no open MRs). Let me check active sessions and recent memory.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p3dzbjgd77a9_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"kinds":["subagent","acp"],"activeMinutes":30,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p3dzbjgd77a9_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/ 2>/dev/null | tail -5 && echo \"---\" && cat /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"No heartbeat state file\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p3dzbjgd77a9_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review && git config --global user.name \"Khuowgn\" && git config --global user.email \"khuowgn@ahvholding.com\" && git config --global commit.template /dev/null && echo \"Git config OK\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1057,"output":375,"cacheRead":10663,"cacheWrite":508,"totalTokens":12603,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776070157000,"responseId":"06